PREFACE.

THE present notes were completed without reference to any other English edition, but the compiler has since re- ferred to Mr. Macleane’s larger work (in the Bibliotheca Classica), and made some useful additions from it. In some instances he has been unable to adopt Mr.Ma01eane's view ; and the latter has hardly done justice to the Freneh commentator (Achaintre).
